            <title><![CDATA[Arknights: Endfield version 1.2 update ‘At the Wake of Spring’ launches April 17]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/04/arknights-endfield-version-1-2-update-at-the-wake-of-spring-launches-april-17</link>
            <guid>1488637</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/mobile/smartphone">Smartphone</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Zhuang Fangyi joins the fray, new areas, and more.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > GRYPHLINE [25 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/hypergryph-network-technology/gryph-frontier/gryphline">GRYPHLINE</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Mountain Contour [14 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/hypergryph-network-technology/mountain-contour">Mountain Contour</a> will release the version 1.2 update for <a title="Genres > Free-to-Play [512 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/free-to-play">free-to-play</a> 3D <a title="Genres > RPG [18,071 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a>  <em><a title="Games > Arknights: Endfield [15 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/arknights-endfield">Arknights: Endfield</a></em>, titled “At the Wake of Spring,” on April 17, the companies announced. <span id="more-1040159"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the update, via GRYPHLINE:</p><blockquote><p>Centered on the core chapter in the Wuling storyline, the update brings major story developments, a high-stakes boss encounter, a new playable Operator, expanded exploration, and meaningful additions to the game’s factory-building systems.</p><p>As tensions rise across Wuling, the story begins with an urgent message from Zhuang Fangyi after Ardashir suddenly appears in the new Marker Stone area, which serves as a critical facility central to Wuling’s stability. At the same time, Nefarith moves into open conflict, setting the stage for players’ first direct battle against her as they push deeper into the crisis threatening Wuling. Already a central figure in the storyline, Zhuang Fangyi will make her playable debut in this update, bringing powerful Electric damage and a combat style that blends lightning-based attacks with swordplay.</p><p>Beyond its new story content, “At the Wake of Spring” introduces additional map and exploration content in Wuling, with Test Area scheduled to open later in the update cycle as players take part in post-disaster restoration, puzzle-solving, and deeper regional exploration. The update also expands the game’s industrial gameplay with a new outpost, new resources, and new production options that deepen Arknights: Endfield’s blend of combat, exploration, and large-scale infrastructure building.</p><p>The update also includes new event content, permanent gameplay updates, a range of quality-of-life improvements across progression, combat, and industrial management, and additional player rewards.</p></blockquote><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>Arknights: Endfield</em> is available now for <a href="https://store.playstation.com/concept/10009205" target="_blank">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via the official launcher and <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/arknightsendfield-f0f167" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>, iOS via <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/arknights-endfield/id6752642477" target="_blank" rel="noopener">App Store</a>, and Android via <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gryphline.endfield.gp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a>.</p><p>Watch a new set of videos below.</p><h2><span>Version 1.2 Update “At the Wake of Spring” Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Arknights: Endfield - Version 1.2 Update &quot;At the Wake of Spring&quot; Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7JYTRe6viwA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="『アークナイツ：エンドフィールド』コアバージョン「春の暁、訪れし時」PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rJksjbnfoiE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="「명일방주: 엔드필드」 메인 챕터 「봄날의 새벽」 버전 PV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zcCSSIowQ3s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</str